<org.eclipse.epf.uma:ArtifactDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmlns:epf="http://www.eclipse.org/epf" epf:version="1.5.1" xmlns:rmc="http://www.ibm.com/rmc" rmc:version="7.5.1" xmi:id="-yBMINvRcRFR_IMRb7R1mnw" name="adoption_plan,{A106554F-3BDA-418D-A1F8-026AE2647AD8}" guid="-yBMINvRcRFR_IMRb7R1mnw" changeDate="2011-05-16T16:27:11.904-0700" version="7.5.0">
  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    This document serves as the implementation plan for rolling out best practices and tools to the organization. It&#xD;
    provides schedule and resource estimates, pilot project training and mentoring estimates for deployment in support of&#xD;
    the key business drivers for the organization.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    This artifact describes all important or critical decisions regarding the proposed implementation of practices and&#xD;
    tools. It describes the overall approach as well detailed implementation plans for deployment.&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <keyConsiderations>This&amp;nbsp;artifact is&amp;nbsp;updated at key stages of the roll-out project to&amp;nbsp;address changing circumstances of the&#xD;
project and evolving requirements.</keyConsiderations>
  <purpose>&lt;a id=&quot;XE_adoption_plan__artifact_definition&quot; name=&quot;XE_adoption_plan__artifact_definition&quot;>&lt;/a>&lt;a id=&quot;Purpose&quot; name=&quot;Purpose&quot;>&lt;/a>&lt;a id=&quot;XE_adoption_plan__purpose_of&quot; name=&quot;XE_adoption_plan__purpose_of&quot;>&lt;/a> &#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    This work product defines the strategy for rolling out process improvements to the organization.&#xD;
&lt;/p></purpose>
  <impactOfNotHaving>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Without this artifact:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        planning details are likely to be poorly defined or inadequate&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        team members will not know what tasks they need to perform&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        the project will be difficult to manage and control&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        it will be hard to adopt capability improvements&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></impactOfNotHaving>
  <reasonsForNotNeeding>&lt;p>&#xD;
    This artifact is typically required in some form on all but the smallest capability improvement projects.&#xD;
&lt;/p></reasonsForNotNeeding>
  <briefOutline>&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;a id=&quot;BriefOutline&quot; name=&quot;BriefOutline&quot;>&lt;/a>This artifact typically contains the following sections:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Adoption goals&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Adoption risks&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Roll-out plan, including a list of pilot projects&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Measurement plan&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Hardware and software topology to support proposed improvements&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Training and mentoring plan&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Migration plan&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Communication plan&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Improvement requests&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Process assurance review reports&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></briefOutline>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:ArtifactDescription>
